<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">首尾均异,即首尾数都不同的两个两位数相乘时,首数积加尾数积再加首尾交叉相乘积的一种求积方法。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(10a+b)(10c+d)=100ac+bd+10ad×b+10bc</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a、c分别是被乘数、乘数十位上的数字，b、d分别是被乘数、乘数个位上的数字。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">35×76=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 35×76</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(30+5)×(70+6)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100×3×7+5×6+10×3×6+10×5×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2100+30+180+350</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2130+530</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2660</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>